My relationship with my parents got progressively worse but I didn't care because he was there for me. In the summer break, he messaged me saying that he 'has to break up with me' because it's 'exhausting to hide things'. I saw him everyday in school. i watch him smile and laugh while I was dying inside and cried everyday. it's been over a year since we ended and I still cry over him.
